column4: A ticket to go see The Amazing Marble Race! But... which one?
A hole-y drink of Qefpedun origin that contains Poup; acid; lava; rotten flesh and 13 different lethal diseases. Approved by Orange.
A special edition of Poup Soop that contains extra Poup; extra acid; extra lava; rotten-er flesh; 14.5 lethal diseases and solid chunks of gold. Approved by Orange.
A special edition of Poup Soop with all the ingredients of regular Poup Soop frozen with solid chunks of ice. Approved by Orange.
A special edition of Poup Soop with twice the ingredients of regular Poup Soop and the essence of Orange. Approved by Orange.
A special edition of Poup Soop with 20% more lava; 20% more acid and electricity generators inside the barrel. Very good conductor of electricity. Approved by Orange.
A special edition of Poup Soop with three times as much lava. Everything including the barrel is flammable and on fire. Approved by Orange.
A special edition of Poup Soop with 6.66 times as much rotten flesh; twice as much acid and 21.25 lethal diseases. Approved by Orange.
The final edition of Poup Soop with three times as much Poup; lava and acid; 47.41394 lethal diseases and several classified ingredients. Approved by Orange.
Contains 50 of each Poup Soop version currently on sale + Poup Bwedd + Poup Stoo + Poup Joos + HATT MANN action figure. Approved by Orange.
